WEBVTT

00:03.495 --> 00:04.722
Welcome to Alpha,...

00:10.091 --> 00:11.951
...the city of a thousand planets,...

00:12.513 --> 00:18.038
...where for hundreds of years, every species has shared their knowledge...

00:18.717 --> 00:20.807
...and their intelligence with each other.

00:21.835 --> 00:22.710
It's paradise.

00:25.293 --> 00:25.748
Amazing!

00:34.313 --> 00:37.025
After centuries of peace and prosperity,...

00:38.995 --> 00:42.368
...an unknown force wants to destroy all we have created.

00:43.714 --> 00:45.109
Agents Valerian and Laureline,...

00:45.204 --> 00:48.109
...you have less than ten hours to find the threat and eliminate it.

00:49.049 --> 00:49.771
Time to get to work.

00:57.211 --> 00:58.131
I taught him how to do that.

